      "text": [
        "2204 - وَ رُوِيَ : «أَنَّ اَلْحَاجَّ مِنْ حِينِ يَخْرُجُ مِنْ مَنْزِلِهِ حَتَّى يَرْجِعَ بِمَنْزِلَةِ اَلطَّائِفِ بِالْكَعْبَةِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2204 - It has been narrated: \"The pilgrim, from the moment they leave their home until they return, is in the status of one performing Tawaf around the Kaaba.\""
        ]
      }
    }
